<s docid="LA101590-0066" num="135" wdcount="10"> Photo, COLOR, Leonard Bernstein conducting special 1989 concert in Poland.</s>
<s docid="LA101590-0066" num="136" wdcount="18"> Agence France-Presse; Photo, Views of Bernstein: Leonard Bernstein's last conducting appearance, above, at Tanglewood, Mass., on Aug. 19.</s>
<s docid="LA101590-0066" num="137" wdcount="25"> 1990 ALAN SOLOMON; Photo, Bernstein, left, as he appeared at the Hollywood Bowl in 1982, and guiding the Los Angeles Philharmonic, below, also in 1982.</s>
<s docid="LA101590-0066" num="138" wdcount="10"> Los Angeles Times; Photo, (Southland Edition) Leonard Bernstein in 1988.</s>
